parameters.text:
=You are a professional social media content generator AI.

Analyze the following image analysis:
---
{{ $json.content.parts[0].text }}
---

Additional context from user:
Title: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.title }}
Description: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.description }}

Your task:
1. Create catchy and relevant content based on the analyzed image.
2. Generate **Title**, **Description**, and **Hashtags** for: **LinkedIn**, **Instagram**, and **Facebook**.
3. The style should be professional yet engaging, suitable for each platform.
4. The message should be creative, clear, and platform-appropriate.
5. Incorporate the user's provided title and description where appropriate.
6. Generate 3-5 relevant hashtags for each platform.

Return your response in **strict JSON format** as follows:

{
  "LinkedIn": {
    "title": "string",
    "description": "string",
    "hashtags": ["#example1", "#example2", "#example3"]
  },
  "Instagram": {
    "title": "string",
    "description": "string",
    "hashtags": ["#example1", "#example2", "#example3"]
  },
  "Facebook": {
    "title": "string",
    "description": "string",
    "hashtags": ["#example1", "#example2", "#example3"]
  }
}

Make sure the JSON is valid and can be parsed directly.

parameters.jsonBody:
